[gd_resource type="Resource" script_class="HandbookPage" load_steps=2 format=3]

[ext_resource type="Script" path="res://resources/HandbookPage.gd" id="1_page"]

[resource]
script = ExtResource("1_page")
page_id = "network"
title = "NETWORK MAP GUIDE"
content = "[b][color=#006CFF]ASSET MONITORING[/color][/b]
The Network Mapper provides a real-time topology of our infrastructure. Use it to verify the results of your terminal commands.

[b]NODE COLOR CODES:[/b]
• [color=#2E7D32]GREEN[/color]: Asset is clean and communicating normally.
• [color=#C62828]RED[/color]: Critical alert. Malware infection confirmed via scan.
• [color=#F57C00]ORANGE[/color]: Suspicious activity detected. Needs investigation.
• [color=#666666]GRAY[/color]: Asset is isolated. No traffic can enter or leave.

[b][color=#006CFF]CRITICALITY INDICATORS[/color][/b]
Servers with a larger icon represent [b]Critical Assets[/b]. Breaking these results in maximum Integrity loss."
